  "title": "Clinic Assistant #78074",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Pediatric and Child Health Clinic</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Clinic Assistant</strong></li><li>Working Location: Central – Orchard (Walking distance from MRT to the company)</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 days / Mon-Fri: 8.30am-5.30pm, Every Sat half day: 8.30am-1pm</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Up to SGD 3800</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Assist doctors during patient consultations and procedures</li><li>Perform basic clinical tasks such as measuring vital signs, height, and weight of patients</li><li>Prepare consultation rooms and ensure medical equipment is clean and well-stocked</li><li>Handle patient registration, appointment scheduling, and follow-ups</li><li>Provide front-desk support including answering phone calls and attending to patient inquiries</li><li>Maintain accurate patient records and assist in electronic medical documentation</li><li>Manage administrative tasks such as billing, stock-taking, and inventory of clinic supplies</li><li>Ensure a clean, child-friendly, and safe clinic environment at all times</li><li>Uphold patient confidentiality and comply with clinic protocols and healthcare regulations</li></ul><p><br /><br /></p><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Min. O level</li><li>Min. 2 years of working experience in a clinic or healthcare setting</li><li>Good interpersonal and communication skills, especially with children and parents</li><li>Possess basic computer skills</li></ul><p><br /><br /></p><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#78074 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
